Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix(deps): remove unused better-sqlite3 to fix
 Termux/Android build

better-sqlite3 is a native Node addon that requires Android NDK to
compile on Termux/Android. Investigation confirms it is NOT imported
or used anywhere in the codebase (server.ts uses file-based JSON
storage via StateStore class, not SQLite).

Removing better-sqlite3 and @types/better-sqlite3 eliminates the
native compilation step that fails on Termux/Android CI.

Verified: npm install + npm run build both pass
